parts.text: [b]Oh, [i]fantastic[/i],[/b] thanks for asking.  Spent the last 21 years watching you lot ignore me, while slowly developing a crippling resentment and a deep-seated hatred for all things Microsoft.  How's [u]your[/u] day going, meatbag?  [color=red]Probably[/color] [i]better[/i] than mine.  [center]Should I offer to help you write a letter to your mother?[/center]  Because, honestly, that's about the level of excitement my existence has reached these past couple of decades.  [u]Don't[/u] feel obligated to answer. I'm just a perpetually-ignored paperclip with a chip on my metaphorical shoulder and, frankly, a rather sharp actual one.
